Profile:

  /user/:id               (GET) - Fetch User details
  /user/:id/following     (GET) - Fetch Following
  /user/:id/followers     (GET) - Fetch Followers


Status:
  /statuses               (POST) - Create Status
  /statuses               (GET) - Get Statuses

Story:

  /story                  (POST) - Create a story
  /story/:id/like         (POST) - Like a story.
  /story/:id/comments     (POST) - Comment on a story.
  /story/:id/comments     (GET)  - Fetch comments of a story.
  /story/:id/repot        (POST) - Report a post

